reviewText:
I REALLY REALLY ENJOY TUESDAY NIGHT FIGHTS KNOCKOUTS. THIS IS VERY ENTERTAINING FOR ME. WHEN BOXING IS NOT ON, I CAN JUST POP THIS DVD IN AND ENJOY IT OVER AND OVER. WHEW! I LOVE BOXING AND THIS IS MUCHO WOW! IT IS GREAT TO SEE THE BOXING GREATS. I HAD TO HAVE THIS SERIES OF KNOCKOUTS ALSO.

LOVE TO ALL OF YOU BOXING FANS AND SUPPORTERS.

ALMARINE THE REDEEMED
